# Email Template Controller Endpoints
# Base URL: http://localhost:3001
# Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

### Create template (protected)
POST http://localhost:3001/email-templates
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

{
  "code": "interview_invitation",
  "subject": "Interview Invitation",
  "content": "Dear {{fullName}}, your interview is at {{interviewTime}}."
}

### Get all templates (protected)
GET http://localhost:3001/email-templates
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

### Get template by ID (protected)
GET http://localhost:3001/email-templates/{{id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

### Update template (protected)
PATCH http://localhost:3001/email-templates/{{id}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

{
  "subject": "Updated Subject"
}

### Delete template (protected)
DELETE http://localhost:3001/email-templates/{{id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}
